I have heard an unusual noise coming from around the general
location of the alternator. I know the sound of an alternator
bearing going south and this sounds a bit different. I've
been meaning to remove the alternator belt so as to eliminate
that as the noise location... That involves removing the gobs
of tape on the engine door though. Perhaps I will do that
after the retest with I drive with poptop edge taped and tail
pipe extended.


> exhaust  smell is worse at speed or when stopped....in any
